{"tid":437673,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[講波]大家仲記唔記得2009-10富咸?","createTime":"2017-10-16T08:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T12:02:47.000Z","uid":153600,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0ebdfde7a866f9a6452ddf2a5cf4de982ec6926d","tid":437673,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:13:07.000Z","msg":"果陣學神教,勁到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隊波完全冇大牌,但踢得超好<br />\n第一屆霸氣杯同羅馬同組,都只係輸一分次名出線<br />\n32強淘汰末代歐洲足協杯盟主薩克達<br />\n16強打祖記,作客輸3比1,以為出硬局<br />\n點知主場大反擊,贏4比1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (不過果場個龍唔係保方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n8強贏德甲冠軍禾夫斯堡,4強再贏果陣仲好勁的漢堡<br />\n決賽打仲有迪基亞,科蘭同阿古路的下體會<br />\n都可以拖到加時先輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟著富咸就開始廢,14年仲降埋班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望學神可以救到水晶宮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e04797d886989f78308b982ce6f8594577cc2b6","tid":437673,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:14:10.000Z","msg":"好懷念呢個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成隊又平又有料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/16/161407_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2F161407_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d4e87155&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fa41ef41983e4a41aaec4b396fcab76a2b8a2fa","tid":437673,"uid":21061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好懷念呢個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成隊又平又有料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/16/161407_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2F161407_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d4e87155&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n艾朗曉士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n漢基蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0540f35b319b52d397fa5eed16ccede1b0b4ae","tid":437673,"uid":111241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:20:14.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9b2849c45a28515d39af1a3da24c2d1f24627cae","tid":437673,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:21:49.000Z","msg":"丹普西，迪比利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422ee18939b771864488dfd1f6c07e1b41c239f7","tid":437673,"uid":38271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:26:34.000Z","msg":"森莫阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n贏祖記主要係大簡發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce167ce7ca58739608beec35745def1b6742af1","tid":437673,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:55:52.000Z","msg":"Dempsey認真係富咸超勁<br />\n可惜12年去熱刺之後就開始渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有zamora,果年比人話一定入到世界杯個squad<br />\n點知決賽傷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6eef42b65edc7f4acd68a74493dfafa1e606216","tid":437673,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"懷念啱啱升班既富咸多D<br />\n有沙夏 馬白蘭基<br />\n記得第一場英超對曼聯輸2:3"},{"pid":"6b69ab36ffa0c7912299a5b123d934a709dbba93","tid":437673,"uid":8122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci